0. Story [30811379 - User can create an account ] description:
==============================================================
User can create an account with the following information:
•	Username 
•	Fist Name,  
•	Suname,
•	Your email, 
•	Re-enter email, 
•	New Password,
•	Gender
•	Birthday 
Please look at attachment of sample of form layout which was taken from Facebook. 
Please use Model Window to show sign-up form:
http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap/javascript.html#modals
Also use form elements from here to compose the form: 
http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap/base-css.html#forms
(note: we already have all bootstrap css and js on our project)


